ot yet been documented in humans; however, the short‐term negative effects have been suggested by several studies.8, 9, 26, 27 These studies focused mainly on the cytotoxic profile of e‐cigarettes and their effects on the respiratory tract,9, 26, 27 central nervous system,9, 10 immune system28, 29 and a few others9, 30, 31 (Table 1).<br />\n<br />\n入面已經講e cig就算冇長期研究，不過短期負效果已經well established，包括肺炎，致癌，影響免疫系統<br />\n<br />\nEpidemiological and clinical studies suggest a strong association between human exposure to PM2.5 and the risk of cardiovascular disease development. Specifically, these studies showed that exposure to PM2.5 from ambient air pollution and/or tobacco smoking is linked to hypertension,156 coronary artery disease,157 myocardial infarction,158, 159 atherosclerosis,156 arrhythmia160 as well as mortality relative risk.161, 162<br />\n<br />\n樓主最關心既心血管病，篇野都講e cig既煙產生PM2.5對心血管好有影響，會導致高血壓，心肌梗塞，血管栓塞，心律不正，從而提高死亡率<br />\n<br />\n其實要做research不如信下有well controlled study同有權威既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"其實簡單講<br />\n唔可以因為某樣野新 冇幾十年research<br />\n就以為冇方法測試樣野有冇害<br />\n<br />\n而事實有好多studies都相信<br />\n就算少左尼古丁，e cig會釋放PG, glycerol, formaldehyde, acetaldehyde 等物質透過呼吸道吸入都係有害<br />\naldehydes更加係致癌物"},{"pid":"d08f111c283f0103f224b234c327d5d9690908f2","tid":1126835,"uid":15739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"樓主講粗口係咪會打冷震"},{"pid":"c1b1e3909eff5698e2bcd4aba4dfe2b89f7a8a64","tid":1126835,"uid":218717,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:55:52.000Z","msg":"自己玩vaping玩咗差唔多2年<br />\n睇完呢到啲comment真係覺得啲人好無知。不過唔緊要，係政府無做好公民教育，仲要醜化電子煙產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主講嘅入煙油電子煙燒出嚟嘅唔係水蒸氣，係由2種&quot;油&quot; 溝埋而燒出嚟，分別係propylene glycol同vegetable glycol，外國可以自己再加nicotine增加衝喉感/似食真煙嘅感覺。<br />\n我自己食咗真煙5年，第一次vape開始就介咗真煙，一黎唔臭，二黎方便，三黎平好多。<br />\n英國政府自己喺5年前已經出report話vaping 比傳統煙傷害減少95%：<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/e-cigarettes-a